name: Stagger
overview: The aliens are coming but they aren't marching left and right like those boring Space Invaders. These villains are bouncing and diving at you from every angle. Keep them at bay and see how far you can progress. Published in 64'er 1991/02, and also in 64'er Sonderheft 79 and in Italy in Tutto C64 n.2 (1992/1993.
